---
title: Tropical Jumbo Salmon and Shrimp with Mango and Hot Pepper Salsa
description: Taste the tropics tonight! Zesty jerk marinade and perky mango salsa brighten up this salmon and shrimp feast! Sweet corn and cilantro rice make a wholesome bed for all this bold goodness.

Ingredients: Jumbo salmon filletss • Shrimp • Mangos • Poblano pepper • Basmati rice • Red onion • Thaw-friendly corn (corn, modified vinegar) • Limes • Mayonnaise  (canola and/or soy oil, liquid whole egg, frozen egg yolk, water, salt, sugar, vinegar, concentrated lemon juice, spice extract, mustard, lactic acid, calcium disodium EDTA) (mustard, egg) • Jerk sauce (water, green jalapeno peppers, white vinegar, garlic, spices, salt, soybean oil, lemon juice, modified corn starch, xanthan gum, natural colour, citric acid, potassium sorbate) • Cilantro.
